1
00:00:00,320 --> 00:00:06,720
♫ <i>Heaven is silent, all is quiet</i> ♫

2
00:00:06,720 --> 00:00:12,820
♫ <i>Yourself in the mirror, can't see clearly in the fog</i> ♫

3
00:00:12,820 --> 00:00:19,200
♫ <i>Floating across the galaxy, across the Netherworld,
injury and parting</i> ♫

4
00:00:19,200 --> 00:00:26,320
♫ <i>Broken dreams are locked deep at the bottom of the sea</i> ♫

5
00:00:27,120 --> 00:00:28,980
♫ <i>Fog and clouds disperse between heaven and earth </i>♫

6
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:33,400
♫ <i>The rain washed the dust away, who is waiting for me</i> ♫

7
00:00:33,400 --> 00:00:39,850
♫ <i>Our fated love can light up the starry sea of time</i> ♫

8
00:00:39,850 --> 00:00:43,100
♫ <i>I come on my own for you, searching for you step by step</i> ♫

9
00:00:43,100 --> 00:00:46,120
♫ <i>Getting into my blood through every breath</i> ♫

10
00:00:46,120 --> 00:00:51,300
♫ <i>Love is reborn on its own</i> ♫

11
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:55,100
♫ <i>I fall towards you</i> ♫

12
00:00:55,100 --> 00:00:58,370
♫ <i>Word for word, you're as bright as a flower</i> ♫

13
00:00:58,370 --> 00:01:01,380
♫ <i>The grief is so vast</i> ♫

14
00:01:01,380 --> 00:01:04,750
♫ <i>The fish leaped and broke out of the cold water</i> ♫

15
00:01:04,800 --> 00:01:11,300
♫ <i>Imagine us enjoying the moonlight at the end of the world</i> ♫

16
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:17,550
♫ <i>A grain of sand growing out of everything</i> ♫

17
00:01:17,550 --> 00:01:25,600
♫ <i>A teardrop falling into the sky...</i> ♫

18
00:01:25,600 --> 00:01:30,060
<i>[The Blue Whisper II]</i>

19
00:01:30,060 --> 00:01:33,100
<i>[Episode 03]</i>

20
00:01:33,100 --> 00:01:36,400
She loves freedom, more than her life.

21
00:01:36,420 --> 00:01:38,760
You trapped her like this, can she be happy?

22
00:01:38,760 --> 00:01:41,300
Well. You don't want her to leave North Abyss, that is okay.

23
00:01:41,360 --> 00:01:43,780
But you don't have to lock her up on Lake Island.

24
00:01:43,780 --> 00:01:46,160
How oppressive.

25
00:01:46,160 --> 00:01:48,760
Can't you each take a step back?

26
00:01:50,860 --> 00:01:54,080
If you love someone, you'll want to make them happy.

27
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:57,080
Or how can you say that it's love?

28
00:02:02,320 --> 00:02:04,840
When did I tell you that I still loved her?

29
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:07,140
You don't need to tell me.

30
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:12,340
Follow your heart.

31
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:18,060
It's late. I have to go back to make soup for Sanyue.

32
00:02:32,180 --> 00:02:35,640
<i>I don't know what has happened to Yunhe.</i>

33
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:37,900
<i>Damn that rope!</i>

34
00:02:37,900 --> 00:02:40,100
<i>Is it so powerful?</i>

35
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:43,240
<i>Let's have a try.</i>

36
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:56,640
Luo Jinsang, don't move.

37
00:02:56,640 --> 00:03:00,700
So I still can't leave your sight.

38
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:09,620
Don't worry.

39
00:03:09,620 --> 00:03:12,300
This time I won't take off your clothes.

40
00:03:15,940 --> 00:03:17,460
Where do you want to go?

41
00:03:17,460 --> 00:03:20,960
Do you really want to stay with me?

42
00:03:22,620 --> 00:03:24,400
You can't close your eyes.

43
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:26,120
I must stay within your sight.

44
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:31,020
If by any chance the spell pulls me back, what if I fall into your heart?

45
00:03:31,020 --> 00:03:33,440
How could you fall into my heart?

46
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:34,840
Do you have any logic?

47
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:38,740
When you close your eyes, what you see is your heart.

48
00:03:39,440 --> 00:03:43,240
What you see is what is on your mind.

49
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:47,220
Well. Will I fall into your heart...

50
00:03:47,220 --> 00:03:49,840
or on your mind?

51
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:59,109
Luo Jinsang, did you do it on purpose?

52
00:03:59,109 --> 00:04:01,840
I'm thinking...

53
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:04,020
your mind...

54
00:04:10,820 --> 00:04:12,540
How is Yunhe?

55
00:04:12,540 --> 00:04:14,140
I've locked her up.

56
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:17,840
Chang Yi, why did you do that?

57
00:04:17,840 --> 00:04:19,700
You know clearly what she wants.

58
00:04:19,700 --> 00:04:22,460
If you give her freedom, you won't lose anything. Why won't you agree?

59
00:04:22,460 --> 00:04:24,360
Listen. Not this time, I'll do it next time.

60
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,840
If it doesn't work next time, I'll do it next time.

61
00:04:25,840 --> 00:04:27,440
One day I will succeed.

62
00:04:27,440 --> 00:04:30,100
Do you know what's going on now?

63
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:31,540
The rumors say Ji Yunhe practices forbidden spells.

64
00:04:31,540 --> 00:04:34,000
Everyone thinks it's she who killed Qing Shu.

65
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:36,340
So many people are spying on her and want to kill her.

66
00:04:36,340 --> 00:04:38,980
Stay here or get killed outside.

67
00:04:38,980 --> 00:04:41,254
If you were her, how would you decide?

68
00:04:57,380 --> 00:05:01,840
Outside North Abyss, Immortal Master and Shunde are so aggressive.

69
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:04,840
Inside North Abyss, the Fox Clan also wants to kill her.

70
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:08,660
It's a big world. But except for the Cloud Quarters,

71
00:05:08,660 --> 00:05:10,700
there is no place for Ji Yunhe to stay.

72
00:05:10,700 --> 00:05:14,460
After all, you still love her.

73
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:17,460
I won't let her go, and I won't let her get killed.

74
00:05:17,500 --> 00:05:19,960
No matter if it's obsession or torture,

75
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:22,740
she must stay alive and suffer.

76
00:05:22,740 --> 00:05:25,780
In the world, only love is difficult to solve.

77
00:05:25,780 --> 00:05:28,620
Xue Sanyue and Li Shu couldn't solve it.

78
00:05:28,620 --> 00:05:31,120
You and Ji Yunhe can't solve it, either.

79
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:34,260
None of you can get out of it.

80
00:05:34,260 --> 00:05:36,920
How about you? Can you get out of it?

81
00:05:39,260 --> 00:05:41,600
Why are you involving me?

82
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:44,080
When did I fall in love with someone?

83
00:05:44,080 --> 00:05:45,900
A doctor does not cure himself.

84
00:05:45,900 --> 00:05:47,960
You also can't get back.

85
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:24,760
<i>Sanyue's favorite food. Don't touch it.</i>

86
00:06:39,140 --> 00:06:42,860
<i>Sanyue's medicine for practicing martial arts. Don't touch it.</i>

87
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:52,740
<i>I do follow Sanyue everywhere,</i>

88
00:06:52,740 --> 00:06:55,980
<i>but if she feels bored and wants to leave here to have a quiet life.</i>

89
00:06:55,980 --> 00:06:58,520
<i>That's fine.</i>

90
00:06:58,520 --> 00:07:01,980
<i>If you don't want me to be the Lynx prince,</i>

91
00:07:01,980 --> 00:07:04,660
<i>I'd like to be your attendant.</i>

92
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:31,127
Why are you smiling?

93
00:07:32,060 --> 00:07:34,040
The view is beautiful.

94
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:38,000
So are you. I want to see you more.

95
00:07:40,700 --> 00:07:43,000
You've seen Chang Yi?

96
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:46,840
Sanyue, I didn't want to keep it a secret. I was afraid that you will get into a fight.

97
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:48,100
Then...

98
00:07:48,100 --> 00:07:49,900
I'm not angry.

99
00:07:51,340 --> 00:07:53,220
How about your talk?

100
00:07:54,900 --> 00:07:56,420
He just deceives himself.

101
00:07:56,420 --> 00:07:57,440
So stubborn.

102
00:07:57,440 --> 00:07:59,160
In his heart, he clearly cares about Yunhe,

103
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:01,180
but he refuses to say anything.

104
00:08:01,180 --> 00:08:02,900
Same goes for Yunhe.

105
00:08:02,900 --> 00:08:04,960
The person you are thinking about is right in front of you.

106
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:08,180
No one explains. Both of them just torture themselves.

107
00:08:08,180 --> 00:08:10,280
Two stubborn lovers are angry with each other.

108
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:11,660
I just hope that...

109
00:08:11,660 --> 00:08:17,140
they won't regret until there is no turning back.

110
00:08:23,740 --> 00:08:26,720
Sanyue, why are you looking at me?

111
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,200
Is there anything on my face?

112
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:32,800
In the past, I always thought that things in the world were either one or the other.

113
00:08:33,820 --> 00:08:37,860
Dilemma or difficulties: those were excuses.

114
00:08:37,860 --> 00:08:40,720
But now when I see Yunhe and Chang Yi's entanglement,

115
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:42,559
I seem to suddenly understand.

116
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:45,260
Everything is not that simple in the world.

117
00:08:45,260 --> 00:08:47,340
There are so many dilemmas,

118
00:08:47,340 --> 00:08:49,520
and it's hard to make a choice.

119
00:08:49,520 --> 00:08:55,220
Li Shu, was it the same situation as this when you saved Qing Ji?

120
00:08:55,260 --> 00:08:58,580
Sanyue, I'm sorry.

121
00:08:58,580 --> 00:09:01,325
- I...
- I don't blame you.

122
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:07,107
I said I don't blame you anymore.

123
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:10,140
What do you mean?

124
00:09:10,140 --> 00:09:12,610
Sanyue, I think it's better to say it clearly.

125
00:09:12,610 --> 00:09:15,720
I will believe what you say.

126
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:18,360
Actually, I don't hate you anymore.

127
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:21,100
I just don't know how to start over.

128
00:09:21,100 --> 00:09:25,820
So I've been indulging in grief and can't extricate myself.

129
00:09:25,820 --> 00:09:29,840
I don't dare say what I think in my mind.

130
00:09:30,940 --> 00:09:33,660
Yunhe and Chang Yi are like that.

131
00:09:33,660 --> 00:09:35,560
I'm in the same situation, too.

132
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:40,500
Between us, it's me who is not brave.

133
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:47,500
After the Ten Directions Formation was broken, I always ignored you.

134
00:09:47,500 --> 00:09:49,420
You always smiled.

135
00:09:49,420 --> 00:09:51,020
You never complained about it.

136
00:09:51,020 --> 00:09:55,200
And you were always with me when I needed your help.

137
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:58,740
During this period, I know you were trying to make up for your mistake.

138
00:09:58,740 --> 00:10:01,720
But I didn't give you any hope.

139
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:05,660
For you, that's too cruel.

140
00:10:05,660 --> 00:10:07,980
No. Not at all, Sanyue.

141
00:10:07,980 --> 00:10:14,300
I'm always thinking that I can pay back what I owe Qing Ji with my life.

142
00:10:14,300 --> 00:10:16,280
What I owe you,

143
00:10:18,020 --> 00:10:19,742
I don't know...

144
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:22,900
I don't know how to pay you back.

145
00:10:22,900 --> 00:10:24,620
You don't owe me anything.

146
00:10:24,620 --> 00:10:27,720
Really. Nothing.

147
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:31,240
I've heard what you said to Chang Yi.

148
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,500
That's right.

149
00:10:32,500 --> 00:10:36,900
Loving someone means that you'd like to make him or her happy.

150
00:10:38,740 --> 00:10:43,580
I don't want you to be anxious and cautious like now.

151
00:10:43,580 --> 00:10:48,180
I'd like to see you still shining and confident.

152
00:10:48,180 --> 00:10:50,440
So you mean that...

153
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:52,760
you still love me?

154
00:10:52,760 --> 00:10:54,575
I love you.

155
00:11:00,560 --> 00:11:04,680
Let's restart our life.

156
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:13,140
♫ <i>We shine like the same light</i> ♫

157
00:11:13,140 --> 00:11:17,040
♫ <i>The same brightness</i> ♫

158
00:11:17,040 --> 00:11:22,480
♫ <i>And become the light together</i> ♫

159
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:38,440
♫ <i>What is left blank is my love confession</i> ♫

160
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:47,560
It hurts.

161
00:11:50,420 --> 00:11:51,560
Immortal Fairy!

162
00:11:51,560 --> 00:11:54,580
Immortal Master ordered that you can't touch your face after treatment.

163
00:11:54,580 --> 00:11:56,180
No. It hurts.

164
00:11:56,180 --> 00:11:58,040
I can't bear that.

165
00:11:58,040 --> 00:12:00,140
Let me go!

166
00:12:03,280 --> 00:12:07,380
Immortal Fairy, this medicine was sent by Master Lin to ease your pain.

167
00:12:14,280 --> 00:12:16,920
Allow him in.

168
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:23,460
Immortal Fairy.

169
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,680
Did you bring this?

170
00:12:25,680 --> 00:12:28,480
I hope it can ease your pain.

171
00:12:29,340 --> 00:12:31,100
What reward do you want?

172
00:12:31,100 --> 00:12:32,640
I don't want anything.

173
00:12:32,640 --> 00:12:34,600
I just have a question.

174
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:35,740
Say it.

175
00:12:35,740 --> 00:12:38,620
There is always a person in my heart that I respect.

176
00:12:38,620 --> 00:12:41,760
But recently, she seems to feel very confused.

177
00:12:41,760 --> 00:12:43,940
What she cherishes was destroyed by others.

178
00:12:43,940 --> 00:12:46,080
I feel so sorry for her.

179
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:51,640
But more desperately, the one she loves doesn't care about her at all.

180
00:12:51,640 --> 00:12:55,680
Even more, she has to suffer a lot every day.

181
00:12:55,680 --> 00:13:01,060
If you were her, do you think it was worth it?

182
00:13:04,900 --> 00:13:06,420
You are dismissed.

183
00:13:06,420 --> 00:13:08,280
Yes.

184
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:13,520
What do you mean?

185
00:13:13,520 --> 00:13:15,620
Immortal Fairy knows what I mean.

186
00:13:15,620 --> 00:13:17,340
Or you wouldn't need to ask others to leave.

187
00:13:17,340 --> 00:13:19,280
I think you've noticed.

188
00:13:19,280 --> 00:13:23,540
If Immortal Master really cared about you, how could he ignore your pain?

189
00:13:23,540 --> 00:13:24,700
No.

190
00:13:24,700 --> 00:13:26,080
Master cares about me.

191
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:28,220
What he did was to cure me.

192
00:13:28,220 --> 00:13:31,360
Even I can make medicine easily to ease your pain,

193
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:33,460
why didn't Immortal Master give it to you?

194
00:13:33,460 --> 00:13:35,200
There is only one reason.

195
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:37,800
Immortal Master doesn't care about your pain at all.

196
00:13:37,800 --> 00:13:41,080
What he cares about is only your appearance.

197
00:13:42,880 --> 00:13:44,120
Shut up!

198
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:46,660
You liar. That's not true.

199
00:13:46,660 --> 00:13:48,460
Yes, what I say doesn't exactly count.

200
00:13:48,460 --> 00:13:50,640
You are the one who feels the pain.

201
00:13:50,640 --> 00:13:54,700
Have you never doubted the reason before?

202
00:13:54,700 --> 00:13:59,200
Have you really never thought if Immortal Master was actually looking at you...

203
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:01,560
or someone else?

204
00:14:11,640 --> 00:14:15,380
<i>How dare you! Why did you change your clothes?</i>

205
00:14:24,560 --> 00:14:28,620
Lin Haoqing, don't try to instigate my hatred towards Immortal Master.

206
00:14:28,620 --> 00:14:32,100
Say one more word, and I'll kill you now.

207
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:37,760
What I said today was because I'm loyal to Immortal Fairy.

208
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:40,000
I just wanted to kindly remind you.

209
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:43,700
It was not only your face that was hurt, but also your heart.

210
00:14:43,700 --> 00:14:46,440
If you want to make sure about what I told you,

211
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:49,680
why don't you go to Immortal Master's Quiet Chamber to have a look?

212
00:14:49,680 --> 00:14:52,420
There is a secret room.

213
00:14:52,420 --> 00:14:55,625
The answer is there.

214
00:14:55,625 --> 00:14:57,625
Get out!

215
00:15:06,860 --> 00:15:10,360
Master, Shunde's temperament is too weird.

216
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:13,360
Maybe she won't follow what you told her but will kill you instead.

217
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:16,800
Why don't we go back to Thousand Flower Valley and plan next?

218
00:15:16,800 --> 00:15:18,640
Her not killing me...

219
00:15:18,640 --> 00:15:21,660
means that she listened to what I said.

220
00:15:21,660 --> 00:15:24,920
She is willful and cruel, but if we take advantage of that,

221
00:15:24,920 --> 00:15:27,860
it's the best weapon to fight against Immortal Master.

222
00:15:27,860 --> 00:15:32,380
Right. What happened to the Spiritual Master who was sent to North Abyss before?

223
00:15:32,380 --> 00:15:33,960
Our spy has entered North Abyss.

224
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:36,900
I believe we will get a message soon.

225
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:44,240
You've gathered so many people here.

226
00:15:44,240 --> 00:15:46,200
Is there something important to discuss?

227
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:47,280
On behalf of them,

228
00:15:47,280 --> 00:15:52,920
today Qing Yao would like to recommend one person to be the leader of North Abyss.

229
00:15:54,060 --> 00:15:57,740
Firstly, we can gather people and reunite the immortals of North Abyss

230
00:15:57,740 --> 00:16:00,640
to maintain harmony and peace well.

231
00:16:00,640 --> 00:16:03,280
Secondly, to intimidate Immortal Master Mansion.

232
00:16:03,280 --> 00:16:07,120
Immortal Master and Shunde will know clearly that North Abyss has a leader.

233
00:16:07,120 --> 00:16:09,240
We won't be bullied by them.

234
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:12,140
We won't let them threaten us at will.

235
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:15,944
Then, who is the perfect candidate in your mind?

236
00:16:15,944 --> 00:16:19,160
You. Merman Prince.

237
00:16:21,920 --> 00:16:24,840
Prince, you don't want to be the leader?

238
00:16:24,840 --> 00:16:27,180
I'm just a guest here.

239
00:16:27,180 --> 00:16:29,240
I'm not suitable for that position.

240
00:16:29,240 --> 00:16:32,240
At that time, we were saved by Prince Chang Yi.

241
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:34,940
Since Father escaped from No Desire Cave, he will need time to recover.

242
00:16:34,940 --> 00:16:37,120
All of the matters of North Abyss were taken over by you.

243
00:16:37,120 --> 00:16:40,320
All immortals were gathered and arranged by you.

244
00:16:40,320 --> 00:16:44,420
You have many ideas and are trustworthy.

245
00:16:44,420 --> 00:16:46,360
I've talked with them about this.

246
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:48,460
We all agree to it.

247
00:16:48,460 --> 00:16:51,840
Prince, please don't decline it.

248
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:53,160
<i>- Right.
- Yeah.</i>

249
00:16:53,160 --> 00:16:59,060
Chang Yi, North Abyss does need a leader now...

250
00:17:02,640 --> 00:17:07,180
<i>Please lead the North Abyss, Master.</i>

251
00:17:15,359 --> 00:17:18,159
Fine. I'll do it.

252
00:17:21,319 --> 00:17:24,219
<i>We pay our respects, Master.</i>

253
00:17:32,360 --> 00:17:38,440
I thought you wouldn't promise them so soon according to your behavior style.

254
00:17:40,200 --> 00:17:41,640
I do not want to be the leader.

255
00:17:41,640 --> 00:17:45,080
And it won't stop me from fighting against Immortal Master

256
00:17:45,080 --> 00:17:47,000
and protecting North Abyss.

257
00:17:48,520 --> 00:17:50,460
Then, why did you promise them?

258
00:17:50,460 --> 00:17:55,160
The North Abyss needs to reunite people and expel darkness,

259
00:17:55,160 --> 00:17:57,940
to no longer fear injustice and coercion.

260
00:17:57,940 --> 00:18:00,640
That's why I must promise to be the leader.

261
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:05,820
As it's so urgent, why did you hesitate?

262
00:18:05,820 --> 00:18:11,000
Actually, everyone knows your ability and sincerity clearly.

263
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:16,020
What you are worried about isn't whether you have the ability to assume the role of Master of the North Abyss.

264
00:18:16,020 --> 00:18:20,760
But you are worried that your private matters will be involved in the business of the North Abyss.

265
00:18:20,760 --> 00:18:23,240
You can't act out of personal considerations

266
00:18:23,240 --> 00:18:28,280
to care about someone or something. Right?

267
00:18:28,280 --> 00:18:33,020
About your entanglement, others can't force you to do anything or help you, either.

268
00:18:33,020 --> 00:18:37,920
So I hope that you can solve that as soon as possible.

269
00:19:14,120 --> 00:19:17,460
Young Lord, are you okay?

270
00:19:18,240 --> 00:19:19,160
I'm fine.

271
00:19:19,160 --> 00:19:21,240
You come here to cure his elixir every day.

272
00:19:21,240 --> 00:19:23,200
You've consumed too much of your power.

273
00:19:23,200 --> 00:19:24,520
It's okay.

274
00:19:24,520 --> 00:19:26,780
My spiritual power is limited.

275
00:19:26,780 --> 00:19:31,680
But it's good enough that Chang Yi is here to lead North Abyss,

276
00:19:31,680 --> 00:19:34,360
or I wouldn't be able to handle both.

277
00:19:34,360 --> 00:19:37,940
Because it's your proposal, Prince Chang Yi agreed to it.

278
00:19:37,940 --> 00:19:40,120
Prince does care for you.

279
00:19:40,120 --> 00:19:44,340
Moreover, which woman in the world is more suitable for Prince than you?

280
00:19:44,340 --> 00:19:47,700
No, it's Master.

281
00:19:47,700 --> 00:19:49,240
Okay.

282
00:19:49,240 --> 00:19:52,840
The next step is the enthronement ceremony of the Master.

283
00:19:52,840 --> 00:19:56,880
This is about the prestige of Chang Yi,

284
00:19:56,880 --> 00:19:58,940
and the morale of all the Immortals here.

285
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:02,100
Be sure to prepare well and don't make any mistakes.

286
00:20:02,100 --> 00:20:03,713
Yes.

287
00:20:14,540 --> 00:20:18,800
Why doesn't this mark get lighter?

288
00:20:20,020 --> 00:20:25,300
Well, will I live my whole life with this mark?

289
00:20:25,300 --> 00:20:27,160
Isn't it good to be alive?

290
00:20:27,160 --> 00:20:30,340
Yeah. It's good to be alive.

291
00:20:30,340 --> 00:20:33,880
But what matters is the way you live.

292
00:20:33,880 --> 00:20:37,760
For my whole life, I've been fighting against my fate.

293
00:20:37,760 --> 00:20:39,960
When I fought against Lin Canglan,

294
00:20:39,960 --> 00:20:44,260
Shunde, or Immortal Master,

295
00:20:44,300 --> 00:20:47,120
I have never given up.

296
00:20:47,120 --> 00:20:49,240
And looking back at these battles now,

297
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:51,880
I won some and also lost some.

298
00:20:51,880 --> 00:20:53,860
Until today,

299
00:20:55,840 --> 00:20:58,640
haven't the battles been fierce?

300
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:05,680
Even so, my life is still my own decision.

301
00:21:05,680 --> 00:21:08,620
I... I don't understand.

302
00:21:08,620 --> 00:21:12,535
A'Ming, I want to take a break.

303
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:23,640
Outside of North Abyss,

304
00:21:24,600 --> 00:21:28,440
with such good scenery, I can only stay here.

305
00:21:36,740 --> 00:21:40,060
Otherwise, I can clean this house.

306
00:21:59,340 --> 00:22:01,460
When did you get here?

307
00:22:01,460 --> 00:22:03,700
It's not time for dinner yet.

308
00:22:03,700 --> 00:22:05,640
What do you want to do?

309
00:22:07,180 --> 00:22:09,500
I took it out and shook it.

310
00:22:09,500 --> 00:22:10,900
Shake it.

311
00:22:10,900 --> 00:22:13,340
I'm done shaking.

312
00:22:13,340 --> 00:22:15,103
Put it back.

313
00:22:16,180 --> 00:22:18,180
Since you're already here,

314
00:22:18,180 --> 00:22:20,560
why don't we start our meal early?

315
00:22:31,400 --> 00:22:34,800
<i>Suicide is too painful and not guaranteed.</i>

316
00:22:34,800 --> 00:22:37,000
<i>Jumping down from this short building,</i>

317
00:22:37,000 --> 00:22:40,400
<i>at best, can only hurt the buttocks.</i>

318
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:42,200
<i>A hunger strike?</i>

319
00:22:42,200 --> 00:22:44,600
<i>But I'm not a mortal.</i>

320
00:22:44,600 --> 00:22:47,400
<i>And the daily scheduled delivery of medicinal food</i>

321
00:22:47,400 --> 00:22:50,200
<i>has to be finished under supervision.</i>

322
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:53,700
<i>How about suffocating myself by holding my breath?</i>

323
00:22:57,000 --> 00:23:00,600
<i>How about setting fire to the house?</i>

324
00:23:00,600 --> 00:23:02,000
<i>Forget it.</i>

325
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:04,100
<i>A'Ming might get involved.</i>

326
00:23:04,100 --> 00:23:09,600
<i>I am afraid that the fire will be extinguished by the big iceberg Changyi before it starts to burn.</i>

327
00:23:16,000 --> 00:23:19,000
The weather has gotten colder in recent days

328
00:23:19,000 --> 00:23:20,800
and my hands and feet are cold.

329
00:23:20,800 --> 00:23:23,600
Get me some more pots of coal.

330
00:23:26,500 --> 00:23:29,000
Is there any red charcoal in the yard?

331
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:30,200
Yes.

332
00:23:30,200 --> 00:23:32,700
Then get me the red charcoal.

333
00:23:32,700 --> 00:23:35,800
I've heard that charcoal is the best.

334
00:23:36,600 --> 00:23:38,600
Remember to get more pots for me.

335
00:23:38,600 --> 00:23:41,400
I can use more when it's cold

336
00:23:41,400 --> 00:23:43,600
and warm up a bit.

337
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:59,000
What's wrong?

338
00:23:59,000 --> 00:24:00,600
It's nothing.

339
00:24:01,600 --> 00:24:04,800
You're getting more and more solemn.

340
00:24:04,800 --> 00:24:08,600
Compared with the past, you have changed a lot.

341
00:24:09,400 --> 00:24:11,200
Thanks to you.

342
00:24:11,200 --> 00:24:15,900
But your face is as good as ever.

343
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:19,600
I like to look at you while eating.

344
00:24:21,000 --> 00:24:24,300
You're a little weird today.

345
00:24:26,600 --> 00:24:28,000
Prince?

346
00:24:30,400 --> 00:24:33,600
Prince, Young Lord Qing Yao wants to talk to you.

347
00:24:35,300 --> 00:24:39,000
Go ahead, I'm done eating anyway.

348
00:24:42,200 --> 00:24:43,800
Chang Yi.

349
00:24:46,800 --> 00:24:50,400
You are the nicest, most beautiful,

350
00:24:50,400 --> 00:24:54,000
gentlest, and kindest person I have ever met.

351
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:58,000
If it were not for the day on the cliff,

352
00:25:00,200 --> 00:25:03,600
I would like you very, very much.

353
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:11,400
I might have spent a lifetime with you.

354
00:25:14,000 --> 00:25:20,800
♫ <i>Hey, think more... think more</i> ♫

355
00:25:24,000 --> 00:25:28,000
♫ <i>Hey, where are you going?</i> ♫

356
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:32,000
♫ <i>Any fool looking up can't keep the light</i> ♫

357
00:25:32,000 --> 00:25:35,900
Are you saying this now for a purpose?

358
00:25:35,900 --> 00:25:39,600
♫ <i>Hey, just follow the flow</i> ♫

359
00:25:39,600 --> 00:25:41,200
No.

360
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:44,200
I just wanted to tell you.

361
00:25:44,200 --> 00:25:48,000
♫ <i>I hope your wishes will come true and you go
to a bright place</i> ♫

362
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:49,900
♫ <i>Away from me, away from sadness</i> ♫

363
00:25:49,900 --> 00:25:51,400
I got it.

364
00:25:52,800 --> 00:25:56,600
Tomorrow, I have something important to take care of

365
00:25:56,600 --> 00:25:58,600
and I can't come over.

366
00:25:58,600 --> 00:26:03,300
Take your medicine and have meals on time, okay?

367
00:26:03,300 --> 00:26:06,800
♫ <i>From now on, you don't have to be scared of anything</i> ♫

368
00:26:06,800 --> 00:26:08,200
I will be good.

369
00:26:08,200 --> 00:26:11,600
♫ <i>Like fireflies chasing the waves</i> ♫

370
00:26:11,600 --> 00:26:13,800
♫ <i>The uncatchable light</i> ♫

371
00:26:13,800 --> 00:26:17,600
♫ <i>is left for one person to recall</i> ♫

372
00:26:17,600 --> 00:26:19,300
It's good.

373
00:26:20,200 --> 00:26:22,800
I've said everything I wanted to say.

374
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:26,400
No more regrets.

375
00:26:27,300 --> 00:26:29,400
♫ <i>Sand is washed away by the rain</i> ♫

376
00:26:29,400 --> 00:26:30,400
It's good.

377
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:34,200
♫ <i>I think you are someplace else, singing happily</i> ♫

378
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:42,000
♫ <i>Never again recalling anything about me</i> ♫

379
00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:47,800
<i>What did she mean by those words just now?</i>

380
00:26:49,400 --> 00:26:51,100
Prince?

381
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:53,400
Prince.

382
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:57,000
Did she just cry?

383
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:58,700
I don't think so.

384
00:26:58,700 --> 00:27:00,800
The backfire is so painful, but she doesn't cry.

385
00:27:00,800 --> 00:27:03,900
Now she has everything she needs, she wouln't cry.

386
00:27:03,900 --> 00:27:06,800
Don't worry. Prince, let's go back.

387
00:27:06,800 --> 00:27:09,000
Tomorrow is your enthronement ceremony.

388
00:27:09,000 --> 00:27:11,800
There are still many things to prepare.

389
00:27:36,800 --> 00:27:39,600
Miss Ji, is there enough charcoal?

390
00:27:45,000 --> 00:27:47,400
That's enough, A'Ming.

391
00:27:47,400 --> 00:27:48,800
You can leave now.

392
00:27:48,800 --> 00:27:51,100
I want to take a nap.

393
00:28:12,000 --> 00:28:16,000
If I can still dream of that nice big tail at the end...

394
00:28:18,800 --> 00:28:21,000
that would be nice.

395
00:28:24,700 --> 00:28:28,000
Master has arrived!

396
00:29:01,000 --> 00:29:07,400
♫ <i>Heaven is silent, all is quiet</i> ♫

397
00:29:07,400 --> 00:29:13,400
♫ <i>Yourself in the mirror, can't see clearly in the fog</i> ♫

398
00:29:13,400 --> 00:29:17,000
♫ <i>Floating across the galaxy, across the Netherworld,
injury and parting</i> ♫

399
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:20,300
<i>If it were not for the day on the cliff,</i>

400
00:29:20,300 --> 00:29:23,800
<i>I would like you very, very much.</i>

401
00:29:23,800 --> 00:29:28,000
<i>I might have spent a lifetime with you.</i>

402
00:29:28,000 --> 00:29:29,600
♫ <i>Fog and clouds disperse between Heaven and Earth </i>♫

403
00:29:29,600 --> 00:29:33,000
♫ <i>The rain washed the dust away, who is waiting for me</i> ♫

404
00:29:33,000 --> 00:29:34,600
Master, what's wrong?

405
00:29:34,600 --> 00:29:40,400
♫ <i>Our fated love can light up the starry sea of time</i> ♫

406
00:29:40,400 --> 00:29:42,200
♫ <i>I come on my own for you, searching for you step by step</i> ♫

407
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:46,800
♫ <i>Getting into my blood through every breath</i> ♫

408
00:29:46,800 --> 00:29:52,800
♫ <i>Love is reborn on its own</i> ♫

409
00:29:52,800 --> 00:29:55,800
♫ <i>I fall towards you</i> ♫

410
00:29:55,800 --> 00:30:00,000
♫ <i>Word for word, you're as bright as a flower</i> ♫

411
00:30:00,000 --> 00:30:04,600
<i>God bless North Abyss, Master!</i>

412
00:30:05,600 --> 00:30:12,000
♫ <i>Imagine us enjoying the moonlight at the end of the world</i> ♫

413
00:30:12,000 --> 00:30:18,400
♫ <i>A grain of sand growing out of everything</i> ♫

414
00:30:18,400 --> 00:30:26,700
♫ <i>A teardrop falling into the sky...</i> ♫

415
00:30:35,800 --> 00:30:38,000
Master, where are you going?

416
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:41,800
This is your enthronement ceremony!

417
00:30:48,700 --> 00:30:50,400
Chang Yi!

418
00:31:26,700 --> 00:31:28,900
<i>You can't leave now.</i>

419
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:48,600
<i>Please stay a little longer.</i>

420
00:31:48,600 --> 00:31:50,500
<i>Who are you?</i>

421
00:32:29,400 --> 00:32:31,700
<i>Am I still alive?</i>

422
00:32:39,400 --> 00:32:42,000
It turns out that the wind blew it out.

423
00:32:43,900 --> 00:32:48,000
It seems that God is joking with me.

424
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:51,200
I was not even allowed to run away.

425
00:32:51,200 --> 00:32:53,200
You want to die?

426
00:32:59,300 --> 00:33:03,000
With a body like this, I'm dead already.

427
00:33:03,000 --> 00:33:08,400
This body is now a cage for me, Chang Yi.

428
00:33:13,520 --> 00:33:15,660
Do you really want to die?

429
00:33:19,200 --> 00:33:21,600
Don't you want to get revenge on me?

430
00:33:26,600 --> 00:33:29,600
Ji Yunhe, who are you to end your life?

431
00:33:29,600 --> 00:33:31,800
Who gave you the guts?

432
00:33:31,800 --> 00:33:33,500
Chang Yi,

433
00:33:34,600 --> 00:33:38,200
the wind on the cliff wasn't cold enough that day, was it?

434
00:33:46,200 --> 00:33:49,000
Isn't it good to do as you're told and run away from the beginning?

435
00:33:49,000 --> 00:33:51,200
Why do you insist on turning back?

436
00:33:51,200 --> 00:33:56,200
My compassion was wasted and I was punished by Shunde.

437
00:33:56,200 --> 00:33:58,800
I was helping you with that sword, Chang Yi.

438
00:33:58,800 --> 00:34:04,100
End your pain in advance so that you wouldn't be sent to Shunde to suffer.

439
00:34:04,100 --> 00:34:06,800
Shut up! Stop saying that!

440
00:34:06,800 --> 00:34:08,700
Now, look at what you've done.

441
00:34:08,700 --> 00:34:12,000
Biting the hand that feeds you and locking me up here.

442
00:34:12,000 --> 00:34:15,000
Taking away even my chance for deliverance.

443
00:34:15,000 --> 00:34:18,400
Your heart is far more ruthless than mine was that day.

444
00:34:18,400 --> 00:34:20,200
Don't you hate me?

445
00:34:20,200 --> 00:34:23,400
Kill me. Kill me!

446
00:34:23,400 --> 00:34:25,400
Kill me and you'll be free!

447
00:34:25,400 --> 00:34:26,400
Kill me!

448
00:34:26,400 --> 00:34:27,600
Do it!

449
00:34:27,600 --> 00:34:28,800
Kill me!

450
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:30,300
♫ <i>Away from me, away from sadness</i> ♫

451
00:34:30,300 --> 00:34:35,400
♫ <i>From now on, there will be no lies, forget the mundane world</i> ♫

452
00:34:35,400 --> 00:34:41,100
♫ <i>Let regret not grow</i> ♫

453
00:34:42,600 --> 00:34:45,800
♫ <i>From now on, you don't have to be scared of anything</i> ♫

454
00:34:45,800 --> 00:34:49,400
You're right, I won't let you die.

455
00:34:49,400 --> 00:34:51,200
I will let you live a miserable life.

456
00:34:51,200 --> 00:34:52,800
♫ <i>The uncatchable light</i> ♫

457
00:34:52,800 --> 00:35:01,200
♫ <i>is left for one person to recall</i> ♫

458
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:11,200
This is good, the intention has been exposed.

459
00:35:11,200 --> 00:35:13,200
I can not die.

460
00:35:13,200 --> 00:35:15,400
The idea has also been seen through.

461
00:35:15,400 --> 00:35:20,200
Ji Yunhe, you deserve it.

462
00:35:22,400 --> 00:35:26,400
Who the hell is in the way of me?

463
00:35:27,400 --> 00:35:29,800
Let's wait and see.

464
00:35:39,800 --> 00:35:41,600
Master?

465
00:35:41,600 --> 00:35:45,300
Master, what's wrong?

466
00:35:45,300 --> 00:35:47,400
You've been so distracted by Ji Yunhe again?

467
00:35:47,400 --> 00:35:49,200
Please go back to the Lingshuang Pavilion soon.

468
00:35:49,200 --> 00:35:52,000
I'll take care of all the things in Cloud Quarters.

469
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:53,400
You don't have to bother.

470
00:35:53,400 --> 00:35:55,600
Running around every day for her is simply...

471
00:35:55,600 --> 00:35:57,600
That's enough!

472
00:36:03,900 --> 00:36:10,400
<i>Ji Yunhe, would you rather die than stay by my side?</i>

473
00:36:14,000 --> 00:36:17,600
All the Immortal friends and masters, I have pacified for you.

474
00:36:17,600 --> 00:36:21,900
They all thought you left because of a sudden physical discomfort.

475
00:36:21,900 --> 00:36:24,200
Things have settled down.

476
00:36:28,200 --> 00:36:31,000
Aren't you supposed to give me an explanation now?

477
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:34,000
Ji Yunhe wanted to kill herself.

478
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:36,000
Kill herself?

479
00:36:36,000 --> 00:36:39,700
The good thing is that she is fine, but she is very weak.

480
00:36:39,700 --> 00:36:42,400
I hope that you can go and treat her.

481
00:36:42,400 --> 00:36:44,100
She made you ruin the enthronement ceremony.

482
00:36:44,100 --> 00:36:47,300
I can even kill her, and you want me to save her?

483
00:36:47,300 --> 00:36:50,600
Sir, please.

484
00:36:51,600 --> 00:36:54,500
Today you left the ceremony without a word,

485
00:36:54,500 --> 00:36:58,000
undermining the authority as the Master of North Abyss.

486
00:36:58,000 --> 00:37:00,000
You brought shame on the Fox Clan.

487
00:37:00,000 --> 00:37:04,300
Young Lord Qing Yao is really sincere to you.

488
00:37:07,100 --> 00:37:11,000
I promise you that I'll check her out.

489
00:37:11,000 --> 00:37:15,600
But I hope you can give everyone an explanation.

490
00:37:15,600 --> 00:37:17,200
Good.

491
00:37:22,000 --> 00:37:26,600
I have told you not to care too much about this merman.

492
00:37:26,600 --> 00:37:29,500
He is not a good man.

493
00:37:35,200 --> 00:37:36,400
How dare you?

494
00:37:37,300 --> 00:37:39,000
Qing Yao trusts you so much,

495
00:37:39,000 --> 00:37:40,600
but you left her alone in the Great Hall

496
00:37:40,600 --> 00:37:43,200
in front of the entire North Abyss, and ran away.

497
00:37:43,200 --> 00:37:46,400
Do you deserve to be the Master of North Abyss?

498
00:37:48,300 --> 00:37:50,600
We can't get over it if you keep silent.

499
00:37:50,600 --> 00:37:54,400
Cousin, let me take care of this matter myself.

500
00:37:54,400 --> 00:37:56,300
You can go now.

501
00:37:57,700 --> 00:38:00,800
Okay. Let's go.

502
00:38:00,800 --> 00:38:03,000
- Let's go.
<i>- Let's go back.</i>

503
00:38:03,000 --> 00:38:04,700
Master.

504
00:38:05,400 --> 00:38:07,800
What happened today?

505
00:38:07,800 --> 00:38:11,300
Today, it's my fault.

506
00:38:11,300 --> 00:38:14,000
Making things difficult for you and your fellow immortals,

507
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:16,200
I am deeply sorry.

508
00:38:16,200 --> 00:38:20,600
But the enthronement ceremony is just a ceremony.

509
00:38:20,600 --> 00:38:22,000
Managing North Abyss,

510
00:38:22,000 --> 00:38:26,200
from the beginning to the end, is not by red tape.

511
00:38:26,200 --> 00:38:29,600
I won't forget the kindness of you and the Fox King.

512
00:38:29,600 --> 00:38:31,200
You have my word.

513
00:38:31,200 --> 00:38:36,900
I, Chang Yi, will protect the stability of North Abyss.

514
00:38:36,900 --> 00:38:39,800
A promise is a promise.

515
00:38:39,800 --> 00:38:42,200
I believe in you.

516
00:38:42,200 --> 00:38:45,000
I don't want you to break faith with the Immortals of North Abyss.

517
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:47,800
You left the ceremony and went to Cloud Quarters,

518
00:38:47,800 --> 00:38:51,400
Mr. Kong Ming and I have concealed it for you.

519
00:38:51,400 --> 00:38:55,600
But this is not the end of the day.

520
00:38:55,600 --> 00:38:58,400
I don't care what's going on in that Cloud Quarters.

521
00:38:58,400 --> 00:39:01,200
But you're so distracted by Ji Yunhe.

522
00:39:01,200 --> 00:39:03,400
How should you deal with it?

523
00:39:03,400 --> 00:39:06,000
She doesn't belong to North Abyss,

524
00:39:06,000 --> 00:39:08,700
and her stay here is not voluntary.

525
00:39:08,700 --> 00:39:14,300
It's me who's looking for troubles for nothing, how can it be dealt with?

526
00:39:14,300 --> 00:39:18,000
If there is a fault, it is my fault.

527
00:39:18,000 --> 00:39:21,200
You can punish me if you want.

528
00:39:21,200 --> 00:39:24,600
I'm not going to punish anybody.

529
00:39:24,600 --> 00:39:26,600
I just want to ask you...

530
00:39:26,600 --> 00:39:29,400
How do you want to treat her in the future?

531
00:39:29,400 --> 00:39:32,400
Since you know that she doesn't belong here,

532
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:34,200
why do you refuse to let her go?

533
00:39:34,200 --> 00:39:36,200
Now that you are the Master of North Abyss,

534
00:39:36,200 --> 00:39:39,000
you should no longer be swayed by her.

535
00:39:39,000 --> 00:39:45,000
Is this the purpose of you pushing me to the throne?

536
00:39:46,200 --> 00:39:47,400
Of course not.

537
00:39:47,400 --> 00:39:51,000
Then what is the connection between her and my governance of North Abyss?

538
00:39:51,000 --> 00:39:55,200
Have I neglected any official business since she came?

539
00:39:57,000 --> 00:39:58,100
No.

540
00:39:58,100 --> 00:40:02,400
From today onwards, I will keep a good eye on her.

541
00:40:02,400 --> 00:40:04,400
I won't let her make any trouble.

542
00:40:04,400 --> 00:40:06,800
Do what you want to do.

543
00:40:06,800 --> 00:40:08,300
I won't make it difficult for you.

544
00:40:08,300 --> 00:40:10,000
I won't force you.

545
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:15,800
All I hope is that you and North Abyss are doing well.

546
00:40:15,800 --> 00:40:17,600
Thanks a lot.

547
00:40:26,800 --> 00:40:30,800
Last time, the picture showing the Immortal order was drawn down as it was.

548
00:40:30,800 --> 00:40:32,400
After pondering these days,

549
00:40:32,400 --> 00:40:34,900
I still can't see what the immortal order refers to.

550
00:40:34,900 --> 00:40:36,400
Your Majesty, don't worry.

551
00:40:36,400 --> 00:40:39,600
An Immortal treasure as it is, it's not easy to penetrate.

552
00:40:49,000 --> 00:40:50,600
It's time to go to Daiyu for cultivation.

553
00:40:50,600 --> 00:40:53,300
Please go together with Lei Ze.

554
00:40:53,300 --> 00:40:56,800
Wait. The cultivation can wait.

555
00:40:56,800 --> 00:40:59,900
Although it can enhance cultivation

556
00:40:59,900 --> 00:41:02,600
and help His Majesty to fight against the Immortal Master in the future,

557
00:41:02,600 --> 00:41:04,400
it is still a very long road.

558
00:41:04,400 --> 00:41:07,700
It's not the most appropriate method at the moment.

559
00:41:07,700 --> 00:41:09,000
Isn't the reaction of this treasure

560
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:13,000
because the comprehension of His Majesty has reached a new level?

561
00:41:13,000 --> 00:41:17,000
So, His Majesty should stay with me for enlightenment.

562
00:41:17,000 --> 00:41:20,400
Right, you are perceptive.

563
00:41:20,400 --> 00:41:23,000
Then why don't you interpret it?

564
00:41:25,200 --> 00:41:27,400
You can go.

565
00:41:31,500 --> 00:41:34,000
Have you penetrated the mystery of the diagram?

566
00:41:34,000 --> 00:41:37,600
Do you want to guide me to this place in the picture?

567
00:41:37,600 --> 00:41:39,200
What are you talking about?

568
00:41:39,200 --> 00:41:42,600
There is no place name or direction on this map.

569
00:41:42,600 --> 00:41:44,000
Is this really a map?

570
00:41:44,000 --> 00:41:47,400
You can go to Daiyu.

571
00:41:47,400 --> 00:41:50,600
You really need to say things in one sentence.

572
00:41:50,600 --> 00:41:53,400
Does Daiyu have anything to do with this map?

573
00:41:53,400 --> 00:41:55,400
His Majesty has been there several times.

574
00:41:55,400 --> 00:41:57,800
But he didn't find any guidelines.

575
00:41:57,800 --> 00:42:01,800
Maybe... this time it will be different.

576
00:42:05,000 --> 00:42:06,600
That's right.

577
00:42:06,600 --> 00:42:13,000
The so-called timing is also about luck.

578
00:42:15,600 --> 00:42:18,400
Then, I'd like to ask you two to go with me.

579
00:42:18,400 --> 00:42:19,700
Yes.

580
00:42:19,700 --> 00:42:21,200
Okay.

581
00:42:27,800 --> 00:42:29,600
Be careful.

582
00:42:29,600 --> 00:42:31,400
Everything has to be wiped clean.

583
00:42:31,400 --> 00:42:34,600
No corner is allowed to be dusty.

584
00:42:38,600 --> 00:42:40,600
Is this house to be demolished?

585
00:42:40,600 --> 00:42:42,400
Master will move in.

586
00:42:42,400 --> 00:42:45,200
Move... Move in?

587
00:42:45,200 --> 00:42:48,800
Master has given an order that in addition to going out for a meeting, patrol,

588
00:42:48,800 --> 00:42:52,400
