592
00:42:57,700 --> 00:42:59,800
A barrier will be added in the middle.

593
00:42:59,800 --> 00:43:02,800
No sound can leak in at all.

594
00:43:02,800 --> 00:43:06,400
Barrier? Where?

595
00:43:07,600 --> 00:43:10,800
Could it be added to my bedside?

596
00:43:10,800 --> 00:43:12,500
Right.

597
00:43:13,800 --> 00:43:15,600
<i>Good for you, Chang Yi.</i>

598
00:43:15,600 --> 00:43:19,900
<i>Isn't it just for spying on me?</i>

599
00:43:23,800 --> 00:43:25,000
Wait.

600
00:43:25,000 --> 00:43:27,300
He's not going to sleep here, is he?

601
00:43:27,300 --> 00:43:29,800
Master said he will move in here.

602
00:43:29,800 --> 00:43:32,600
He will stay over during the day and at night.

603
00:43:32,600 --> 00:43:34,800
But isn't this a lake-centered courtyard?

604
00:43:34,800 --> 00:43:37,400
It's so isolated. It's not appropriate for him to come over.

605
00:43:37,400 --> 00:43:38,600
You must be joking.

606
00:43:38,600 --> 00:43:41,200
Wherever the Lord goes, the center is naturally.

607
00:43:41,200 --> 00:43:43,200
Why is it isolated?

608
00:43:44,000 --> 00:43:46,300
Prepare the bed for Master.

609
00:43:46,300 --> 00:43:48,000
<i>Yes.</i>

610
00:43:49,900 --> 00:43:53,400
Ji Yunhe, see?

611
00:43:53,400 --> 00:43:55,600
You're really good.

